        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down. | Bromley. | Kent. S.E.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>May 8</date>
                    <salute>My dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I write one line to say that I have received, with my thanks, your Bill of <hi rend="superscript">£</hi>372, &amp; to say that your note is quite satisfactory.<ref target="#foot.f2"/> I am sorry to have caused you trouble. I hope to be in London before very long &amp; will call</p>
<p>In Haste | My dear Sir | Yours very sincerely | C. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
        </div>

        

        

